The paper deals with machine learning models and deep neural networks for image segmentation and captioning tasks, which are typically associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also discusses multi-task learning (MTL) and Bayesian formulations, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper mentions the use of multi-modal techniques, which can be associated with multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
